    "However, the development of HDT is still in its infancy.",
    "Despite the growing number of publications discussing HDT, it can still be observed that the existing research lacks an in-depth analysis of HDT from the perspective of generic frameworks, technologies, applications, and challenges.",
    "Thus, we intend to analyze the status of HDT research, propose a comprehensive architecture for organizing the HDT, present the state of the art of core technologies and applications of HDT, and discuss various potential trends and challenges related to the development of HDT.",
    "The main contributions of this paper can be summarized as follows:1.",
    "Present a comprehensive literature review on the current state-of-the-art in HDT, comparative analysis of the research focus, technological advantages, and existing shortcomings to provide a typical research framework for the field.2."
